  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA62">
<l>ētokku mētovvā tētāku mētākā</l>
<l>tētokku meṉpataṉai yāraṟivār - pūtappāl</l>
<l>vilvēṭa ṉāki vicayaṉō ṭēṟṟanāḷ</l>
<l>valvēṭa ṉāṉa vaṭivu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Who knows how to say what is similar, what is not similar,</l>
<l>what will become, what will not become, what is similar</l>
<l>– to the form that is of the strong hunter on the day he engaged</l> 
<l>with Vicayaṉ as a bow hunter, in a former time?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
